Package com.example.networkmeup.view.Login.LoginEmployer

Interface LoginEmployerView

All Known Implementing Classes:
LoginEmployerActivity, LoginEmployerViewStub
public interface LoginEmployerView
This interface defines the methods to be implemented by the LoginEmployerActivity. It provides a contract for the presenter to interact with the activity to handle employer login functionality.
